title: Someone has just loged my account on league when i was on my other account
body: i have no idea what just happen and i was logging onto my low level account that im gonna be leveling and i found that someone has logged this account an messed with  some of my masteries pages

replies.body: First thing you'll want to do is change your password for the account and the email associated with the account. If you notice anything else out of place that isn't your masteries, hit us up in a [**support ticket.**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)
